<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.8">
<l>veḷiya caṅkoṉ ṟuṭaiyāṉaip pītaka vāṭai yuṭaiyāṉai</l>
<l>yaḷinaṉ kuṭaiya tirumālai yāḻi yāṉaik kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>kaḷivaṇ ṭeṅkuṅ kalantāṟpōṟ kamaḻpūṅ kuḻalkaḷ taṭantōḷmēṉ</l>
<l>miḷira niṉṟu viḷaiyāṭa viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see He with a white conch, He with yellow garments?</l>
<l>Tirumāl with a fine grace, the Discus-bearer?</l>
<l>We saw Him in Bṛndāvana with the pretty, fragrant locks</l>
<l>shine and constantly play on [His] large shoulders,</l>
<l rend="indent">as if intoxicated bees had spread everywhere!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
